{"tid":660079,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁詠琪：「老公是我最堅強的後盾！」","createTime":"2018-05-10T11:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T04:31:53.000Z","uid":35964,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"85d480e244723f8fc805b0f140dd2e0658126f82","tid":660079,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:35:54.000Z","msg":"心境有着如斯轉變，全因人生中遇到了很多影響自己至深的人。近年影響她最多的一定是丈夫Sergio，八年前剛失戀的時候，她獨自往西班牙旅遊，在朋友的聚會上邂逅彷彿失散已久的靈魂伴侶，二人一拍即合，交往不久就「閃婚」。談到老公便嘴角上揚的她說自己的愛情可算是一見鍾情：「我不會用觸電來形容，但第一次相遇已經有種好熟悉，似曾相識的感覺。他很自信，同時也很謙虛、很誠懇。」<br />\n<br />\n丈夫是她最堅強的後盾，同時亦令曾經很保護自己的梁詠琪放下執着，漂泊的心靈終於靠岸。「認識他之後，我不再因為藝人的身份而做事有太多顧慮和執着，他的輕鬆和自信令我發現，原來光明正大地做回原本的梁詠琪，可以是件很容易的事，這方面他是我的榜樣，只要所有事情都是憑良心做，就可以天天快樂無憂。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/elle_star/gigi-leung-cover-story/20180329-elle-gigi-leung189008n01/25444407-1-chi-HK/20180329-elle-Gigi-Leung189008n01_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Felle_star%2Fgigi-leung-cover-story%2F20180329-elle-gigi-leung189008n01%2F25444407-1-chi-HK%2F20180329-elle-Gigi-Leung189008n01_img_885_590.jpg&h=259ddf98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b51137746907babca6e0c457b62cc09d24289c1f","tid":660079,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">西</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6ad940209dca39f532e716bb51dd0ac1f5b8a9f1","tid":660079,"uid":14460,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">西</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">楚</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0aabe612745246dd35aaa5bc361672868542535c","tid":660079,"uid":104218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited